 Universal 8bit Graphics Library V2

 Path: esp32/components/u8g2
 Upstream: https://github.com/olikraus/u8g2
 License: Two-clause BSD license, fonts under other licenses
          (see project for details)

 Library has been modified as necessary for project integration purposes.

******************************************************************************

 zlib Data Compression Library

 Path: esp32/components/zlib
 Upstream: https://zlib.net/
 License: BSD-style (see project for details)

 A subset of the library, only containing pieces necessary for integration,
 has been included.

******************************************************************************

 SNTP client module (from lwIP)

 Path: esp32/components/my_sntp
 Upstream: https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/components/lwip/apps/sntp
 License: BSD

 This is the SNTP implementation from Espressif's ESP-IDF (via lwIP),
 modified to prevent symbol name conflicts and to add features
 necessary for this application. If those features are ever added to
 the upstream version, then this one will be removed.

******************************************************************************
